}}{{TIDTOC|adapter}} ==Overview== The particular unit used for this entry is a UH-204(GOLD).
This device was originally listed on '''Aten'''s site [http://web.archive.org/web/20020610005417/http://www.aten-usa.com/products/product.php?Item=UH204 as OEM/ODM only], but that [http://web.archive.org/web/20021012052326/http://www.aten-usa.com/products/product.php?Item=UH204 was later omitted]. :Presumed 2002 release year
"0PB4-0095-B" is silkscreened on the top of the board. :"ZUH24-A-31" and "ZO5-320070000941AD" is printed on a label affixed to the bottom of the board.
This device is using '''ACON''' USB connectors.
